metadata.name: STRINGS OF LOVE
metadata.description:
Strings Of Love

⭕️MINT 2 atleast for BURN & REDEEM(There will be a 3d art)

Strings of Love can be described as celestial strings connecting two celestial bodies, 
symbolizing their unbreakable bond and love for each other, like the stars in the universe.

The aurora lights is a mesmerizing display of vibrant colors in the sky, representing the passion and energy of a couple's love.

The bond they are sharing in space and he is dedicating a music for her which defines enjoying every moment with your close people wherever you are.
